data.description: HERE IT IS!  If you're looking for the most immaculate home on the market today...this move in ready home is a show stopper!  5 Beds, 3 Baths, gorgeous large back yard, and a front porch to enjoy those warm Carolina summers with a glass of sweet tea. The outdoor living doesn't stop there...with both a deck and a patio you will enjoy a large private yard just waiting for your gardening skills. Imagine hosting in a kitchen that Bobby Flay would love.  When the fall arrives prepare yourself to cuddle up near the gas fireplace! Kitchen features crisp white cabinets, durable quartz counters, glass mosaic tile backsplash, and hand selected light fixtures that draw you in.  Primary suite to get away from the stress of the day invites you to relax and rejuvenate yourself.  A first floor additional bedroom that welcomes guests plus an office too!? And so close to the Copper District.
